<plot>Paul Angone thought he had it all figured out when he graduated from college. But the harsh reality of just trying to stay alive began to envelop him. To gain wisdom on how to deal with the pressures of not knowing what do to with his life, Paul begins at the end by asking the elderly for help. Seniors offer their stories and advice in this documentary short that spans generations.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?391899</url></doc>
